---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Social Proof for Home Organizers — Collect & Display Client Testimonials | SocialProof.dev" description="SocialProof helps home organizers collect client testimonials and display them on their website. Show potential clients what transformation looks like — free to start.">
  <main class="for-page">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="badge">For Home Organizers</div>
        <h1>Turn satisfied clients into a steady stream of new bookings</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Home organizing is a referral business — but word of mouth doesn't show up on your website. SocialProof helps you capture those glowing reactions and turn them into your most convincing sales tool.</p>
        <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/register" class="btn-primary">Start free — no credit card</a>
        <p class="micro">Free forever for 1 active widget</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="problem">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>The "before and after" is powerful. The testimonial is even more powerful.</h2>
        <p>Clients gasp when they see their pantry transformed. They tell their friends. But that enthusiasm rarely makes it onto your website — because asking for a written review feels awkward, and most clients never follow through.</p>
        <p>Meanwhile, a prospect is browsing your site, looking for a reason to trust you with their home. A single heartfelt testimonial — "She transformed my kitchen in 4 hours and I've actually kept it organized for 6 months" — is worth more than any before/after photo.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="benefits">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Built for organizers who book through trust</h2>
        <div class="benefits-grid">
          <div class="benefit">
            <h3>🔗 One link, zero friction for your client</h3>
            <p>Send your collection link the moment the session ends — when they're still amazed at the result. They click, fill 3 fields, done. No login, no app.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="benefit">
            <h3>✅ You approve before it goes live</h3>
            <p>Every testimonial comes through your dashboard first. You choose what to display. Privacy stays yours.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="benefit">
            <h3>📍 Works on any site</h3>
            <p>Squarespace portfolio, WordPress blog, Wix, or a plain HTML page — one script tag and your widget is live anywhere.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="benefit">
            <h3>⭐ Optional star ratings</h3>
            <p>Let clients add a 5-star rating alongside their text review. Great for building an SEO-indexed testimonials page.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="benefit">
            <h3>📸 Photo uploads</h3>
            <p>Clients can attach a profile photo to put a face on their testimonial. Makes it real, makes it trust-worthy.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="benefit">
            <h3>📱 Mobile-optimized widget</h3>
            <p>Your widget looks beautiful on every device. Prospects browsing on their phone see your best social proof, not a broken widget.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sample-widget">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>See what it looks like</h2>
        <div class="widget-preview">
          <blockquote>
            <p>"I was skeptical — my home has been 'chaotic' for 15 years. In one afternoon, Jenna transformed my closet and gave me a system I can actually maintain. Three months later, it's still perfect. Worth every penny and more."</p>
            <footer>— Rachel T., Seattle WA</footer>
          </blockquote>
        </div>
        <p>Your real testimonials, displayed like this, on your actual website.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="how-it-works">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Setup takes 10 minutes</h2>
        <ol class="steps">
          <li><strong>Create your free account</strong> at app.socialproof.dev</li>
          <li><strong>Get your collection link</strong> — one URL you send to clients</li>
          <li><strong>Share it after every session</strong> — text, email, your follow-up survey</li>
          <li><strong>Approve testimonials</strong> in your dashboard</li>
          <li><strong>Embed the widget</strong> on your site with one line of code</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="faq">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Common questions</h2>
        <div class="faq-list">
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Do my clients need to create an account?</h3>
            <p>No. They open your link, fill out the form, and they're done. Zero friction, which is why response rates are so much higher.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>What if a client submits something I don't want to publish?</h3>
            <p>Nothing goes live without your approval. You review each testimonial in your dashboard and decide what to show.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Can I collect testimonials from past clients?</h3>
            <p>Absolutely. Send your collection link to your whole client list and catch up on months of missed testimonials at once.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>I use Squarespace / Wix / Webflow — does it work?</h3>
            <p>Yes. Paste one script tag anywhere in your site's HTML and the widget appears. Works with every platform that allows custom code.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Ready to let your clients do your marketing?</h2>
        <p>Join organizers collecting real testimonials and converting more prospects into bookings.</p>
        <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/register" class="btn-primary">Start free today</a>
        <p class="micro">Free forever for 1 active widget · No credit card required</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

<div class="footer-links" style="margin-top:2rem;padding-top:1.5rem;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;font-size:0.9rem;">
